  <section class="bg-white border-b py-8">
    <div class="container max-w-5xl mx-auto m-8">
      <h1 class="w-full my-2 text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-center text-gray-800">
        移行手順
      </h1>

      <div class="w-full mb-4">
        <div class="h-1 mx-auto gradient w-64 opacity-25 my-0 py-0 rounded-t"></div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center">
       <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 text-center">
          <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/login.jpg', class: "w-100% sm:h-64 mx-auto" %>
          <a class="underline text-xs italic font-thin tracking-tighter text-gray-400" href="https://www.freepik.com/vectors/website">
            Website vector created by stories - www.freepik.com
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="w-5/6 sm:w-1/2 p-6">
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
              Qiitaアカウントでログイン
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
              Qiitaのアカウントでログインができます。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center">
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6 text-center">
          <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/migrate_article.jpg', class: "w-100% sm:h-64 mx-auto" %>
          <a class="underline text-xs italic font-thin tracking-tighter text-gray-400" href="https://www.freepik.com/vectors/website">
            Website vector created by stories - www.freepik.com
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
          <div class="align-middle">
            <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
              Zenn形式の設定
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
              自分が執筆してきたQiita記事をZenn形式に変換するための設定ができます。
              <br />
              <br />
              Zenn形式とは:

              <a class="text-pink-500 underline" href="https://zenn.dev/zenn/articles/zenn-cli-guide">zenn.dev#執筆の仕方</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center">
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6 text-center">
          <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/download.jpg', class: "w-100% sm:h-64 mx-auto" %>
          <a class="underline text-xs italic font-thin tracking-tighter text-gray-400" href="https://www.freepik.com/vectors/website">
            Website vector created by stories - www.freepik.com
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
          <div class="align-middle">
            <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
              記事ファイルをダウンロード
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
              設定した形式でファイルをダウンロードして、zipで解凍してください。
              <br />
              <br />
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center">
        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6 text-center">
          <%= image_pack_tag 'media/images/upload_zenn.png', class: "w-100% sm:h-64 mx-auto" %>
          <a class="underline text-xs italic font-thin tracking-tighter text-gray-400" href="https://www.freepik.com/vectors/website">
            Website vector created by stories - www.freepik.com
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full sm:w-1/2 p-6 mt-6">
          <div class="align-middle">
            <h3 class="text-3xl text-gray-800 font-bold leading-none mb-3">
              記事をzennにアップロード
            </h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
              ダウンロードしたファイルをGithubにpushし、zennと連携することで一括アップロードができます。
              <br />
              <br />
              アップロード方法:

              <a class="text-pink-500 underline" href="https://zenn.dev/zenn/articles/connect-to-github">zenn.dev#GitHub連携</a>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="bg-white border-b py-8">
    <div class="container mx-auto flex flex-wrap pt-4 pb-12">
      <h1 class="w-full my-2 text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-center text-gray-800">
        設定できること
      </h1>
      <div class="w-full mb-4">
        <div class="h-1 mx-auto gradient w-64 opacity-25 my-0 py-0 rounded-t"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow">
          <div class="w-full font-bold text-4xl text-gray-800 px-6 p-4">
            slag
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6">
            zennの記事のslug（スラッグ）という、ユニークなIDのような文字列を設定できます。
          </p>
          <div class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5">
            <div class="px-6">
              <ul class="list-disc ">
                <li>Qiitaの記事ID(デフォルト)</li>
                <li>任意のslag</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-none mt-auto bg-white rounded-b rounded-t-none overflow-hidden shadow p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-start">
            <a class="mx-auto lg:mx-0 hover:underline gradient text-white font-bold rounded-full my-6 py-4 px-8 shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://zenn.dev/zenn/articles/what-is-slug" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              詳しく
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow">
          <div class="w-full font-bold text-4xl text-gray-800 px-6 p-4">
            title
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6">
            記事のタイトルを変更できます。
          </p>
          <div class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5">
            <div class="px-6">
              <ul class="list-disc ">
                <li>Qiitaの記事タイトル(デフォルト)</li>
                <li>任意のtitle</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-none mt-auto bg-white rounded-b rounded-t-none overflow-hidden shadow p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-start">
            <a class="mx-auto lg:mx-0 hover:underline gradient text-white font-bold rounded-full my-6 py-4 px-8 shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://zenn.dev/zenn/articles/zenn-cli-guide#%E8%A8%98%E4%BA%8B%E3%81%AE%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%90" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              詳しく
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow">
          <div class="w-full font-bold text-4xl text-gray-800 px-6 p-4">
            emoji
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6">
            記事のアイキャッチとして使われる絵文字（1文字だけ）を設定できます。
          </p>
          <div class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5">
            <div class="px-6">
              <ul class="list-disc ">
                <li>任意のemoji</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-none mt-auto bg-white rounded-b rounded-t-none overflow-hidden shadow p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-start">
            <a class="mx-auto lg:mx-0 hover:underline gradient text-white font-bold rounded-full my-6 py-4 px-8 shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://zenn.dev/zenn/articles/zenn-cli-guide#%E8%A8%98%E4%BA%8B%E3%81%AE%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%90" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              詳しく
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow">
          <div class="w-full font-bold text-4xl text-gray-800 px-6 p-4">
            type
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6">
            記事のタイプを設定できます。（tech: 技術記事 / idea: アイデア記事）
          </p>
          <div class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5">
            <div class="px-6">
              <ul class="list-disc ">
                <li>tech(デフォルト)</li>
                <li>任意のtype</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-none mt-auto bg-white rounded-b rounded-t-none overflow-hidden shadow p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-start">
            <a class="mx-auto lg:mx-0 hover:underline gradient text-white font-bold rounded-full my-6 py-4 px-8 shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://zenn.dev/tech-or-idea" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              詳しく
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow">
          <div class="w-full font-bold text-4xl text-gray-800 px-6 p-4">
            topics
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6">
            topics(タグ)を設定できます。
          </p>
          <div class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5">
            <div class="px-6">
              <ul class="list-disc ">
                <li>Qiitaの記事のタグ(デフォルト)</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-none mt-auto bg-white rounded-b rounded-t-none overflow-hidden shadow p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-start">
            <a class="mx-auto lg:mx-0 hover:underline gradient text-white font-bold rounded-full my-6 py-4 px-8 shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://zenn.dev/zenn/articles/zenn-cli-guide#%E8%A8%98%E4%BA%8B%E3%81%AE%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%90" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              詳しく
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="w-full md:w-1/3 p-6 flex flex-col flex-grow flex-shrink">
        <div class="flex-1 bg-white rounded-t rounded-b-none overflow-hidden shadow">
          <div class="w-full font-bold text-4xl text-gray-800 px-6 p-4">
            published
          </div>
          <p class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6">
            記事の公開設定ができます。
          </p>
          <div class="text-gray-800 text-base px-6 mb-5">
            <div class="px-6">
              <ul class="list-disc ">
                <li>公開(デフォルト)</li>
                <li>非公開</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-none mt-auto bg-white rounded-b rounded-t-none overflow-hidden shadow p-6">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-start">
            <a class="mx-auto lg:mx-0 hover:underline gradient text-white font-bold rounded-full my-6 py-4 px-8 shadow-lg focus:outline-none focus:shadow-outline transform transition hover:scale-105 duration-300 ease-in-out" href="https://zenn.dev/zenn/articles/zenn-cli-guide#%E8%A8%98%E4%BA%8B%E3%81%AE%E4%BD%9C%E6%88%90" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              詳しく
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  
  
</div>